%20from%20commenting%20on%20the%20matter%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727322720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F3f88hnb8_ashok-gehlot_625x300_21_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrouble-for-ashok-gehlot-ex-aide-points-to-him-in-rajasthan-phone-tapping-case-6651933%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20aide's%20statement%20to%20Delhi%20Police%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20phone-tapping%20case%20can%20turn%20the%20heat%20on%20Congress%20veteran%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrouble-for-ashok-gehlot-ex-aide-points-to-him-in-rajasthan-phone-tapping-case-6651933%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BSE%20Sensex%2C%20Nifty50%20open%20in%20green%3B%20near%20lifetime%20highs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727322502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113685531%2Cimgsize-113470.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fstock-market-today-bse-sensex-nifty50-september-26-2024-dalal-street-indian-equities-global-markets%2Farticleshow%2F113685194.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stock%20market%20today%3A%20BSE%20Sensex%20and%20Nifty50%2C%20the%20Indian%20equity%20benchmark%20indices%2C%20opened%20in%20green%20on%20Thursday.%20Both%20BSE%20Sensex%20and%20Nifty50%20were%20just%20short%20of%20their%20lifetime%20high.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'You%20Have%20Rs%2015%2C000%20Crore%20Due%20Why%20Only%20Settle%20BCCI's'%3A%20Top%20Court%20To%20Byju's%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20questioned%20why%C2%A0crisis-hit%20ed-tech%20major%20Byju's%20chose%20to%20settle%20its%20dues%20only%20with%20the%20BCCI%20despite%20being%C2%A0in%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore%20debt.%20The%20insolvency%20appellate%20tribunal%20NCLAT%20did%20not%20apply%20its%20mind%20while%20closing%20insolvency%20proceedings%20against%20the%20firm%2C%20the%20top%20court%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Company%20Law%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20(NCLT)'s%20relief%20for%20Byju's%20came%20on%20August%202%20after%20it%20approved%20Rs%20158.9%20crore%20dues%20settlement%20with%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20came%20as%20a%20huge%20relief%20for%20founder%20Byju%20Raveendran%2C%20which%20put%20him%20back%20in%20control.%20But%20the%20relief%20didn't%20last%20long%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20August%2014%20staying%20its%20operations%20on%20an%20appeal%20by%20Glas%20Trust%20Company%20LLC%2C%20an%20US-based%20creditor%20of%20the%20edtech%20firm.%20The%20top%20court%20had%20asked%20the%20BCCI%20to%20keep%20the%20amount%20it%20received%20as%20part%20of%20the%20settlement%20in%20a%20separate%20bank%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20company%20is%20in%20debt%20of%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore.%20When%20the%20quantum%20of%20the%20debt%20is%20so%20large%2C%20can%20one%20creditor%20(BCCI)%20walk%20away%20saying%20one%20promoter%20is%20ready%20to%20pay%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20D%20Y%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justices%20J%20B%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20hinted%20that%20it%20may%20send%20the%20case%20back%20to%20the%20appellate%20tribunal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20pick%20up%20BCCI%20and%20settle%20with%20them%20only%20from%20your%20personal%20assets...The%20NCLAT%20accepts%20this%20all%20without%20applying%20its%20mind%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20hearing%20on%20the%20US%20firm's%20appeal%20began%20Wednesday.%20It%20will%20resume%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArguing%20for%20the%20Glas%20Trust%20LLC%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Shyam%20Divan%20said%20the%20NCLAT%20shouldn't%20have%20stopped%20the%20insolvency%20proceedings%20against%20Byju's%20after%20the%20BCCI%20claimed%20the%20settlement%20amount%20and%20called%20the%20settlement%20money%20paid%20to%20the%20BCCI%20%26quot%3Btainted%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocates%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%20and%20NK%20Kaul%2C%20representing%20Byju's%2C%20said%20the%20money%20was%20paid%20by%20Riju%20Raveendran%2C%20brother%20of%20Byju%20Raveendran%2C%20from%20his%20personal%20assets%20and%20there%20was%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20NCLAT%20closing%20the%20insolvency%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20BCCI%2C%20echoed%20the%20same%20stand%20and%20said%20the%20cricket%20board%20got%20its%20claim%20from%20the%20personal%20assets%20of%20a%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20firm%20had%20earlier%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20interim%20resolution%20professional%20(IRP)%20dealing%20with%20the%20insolvency%20case%20against%20Byju's%20had%20wrongly%20removed%20it%20from%20the%20committee%20of%20creditors.%20It%20had%20said%20it%20held%2099.41%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20the%20company%2C%20which%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20zero%20by%20the%20IRP%20while%20those%20with%200.59%20per%20cent%20stake%20now%20have%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20%26quot%3Bteam%20sponsor%20agreement%26quot%3B%20between%20Byju's%20and%20the%20BCCI%2C%20which%20was%20signed%20in%202019%2C%20the%20edtech%20firm%20had%20to%20pay%20a%20sponsorship%20fee%20for%20the%20exclusive%20rights%20to%20display%20its%20brand%20on%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team's%20kit.%20The%20payments%20continued%20till%202022%2C%20but%20after%20that%2C%20Byju's%20had%20defaulted%20on%20the%20sponsorship%20fee%20of%20Rs%20158.9%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20met%20its%20obligations%20till%20the%20middle%20of%202022%20but%20defaulted%20on%20subsequent%20payments%20of%20Rs%20158.9%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727322420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F3ldcdekg_byju-raveendran-_625x300_14_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-questions-tribunal-order-on-byjus-bcci-settlement-without-apply-mind-6651683%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20questioned%20whycrisis-hit%20ed-tech%20major%20Byju's%20chose%20to%20settle%20its%20dues%20only%20with%20the%20BCCI%20despite%20beingin%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore%20debt.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-questions-tribunal-order-on-byjus-bcci-settlement-without-apply-mind-6651683%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20urges%20Apple%20to%20decrypt%20phones%20of%20accused%20assassins%2C%20aid%20FBI%20probe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727322327000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113685656%2Cimgsize-39096.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-urges-apple-to-decrypt-phones-of-accused-assassins-aid-fbi-probe%2Farticleshow%2F113684464.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20has%20urged%20Apple%20to%20aid%20the%20FBI%20in%20decrypting%20phones%20linked%20to%20assassination%20plots%20against%20him.%20The%20FBI%20is%20struggling%20to%20access%20certain%20apps%20and%20devices%20related%20to%20the%20investigation.%20Trump%20also%20criticized%20President%20Biden%20for%20not%20addressing%20threats%20from%20Iran%2C%20suggesting%20a%20strong%20retaliatory%20stance%20if%20he%20were%20president.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20urges%20A