that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmiramurati%2Fstatus%2F1839025700009030027%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20shared%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EHi%20all%2C%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20have%20something%20to%20share%20with%20you.%20After%20much%20reflection%2C%20I%20have%20made%20the%20difficult%20decision%20to%20leave%20OpenAl.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMy%20six-and-a-half%20years%20with%20the%20OpenAl%20team%20have%20been%20an%20extraordinary%20privilege.%20While%20I'll%20express%20my%20gratitude%20to%20many%20individuals%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20I%20want%20to%20start%20by%20thanking%20Sam%20and%20Greg%20for%20their%20trust%20in%20me%20to%20lead%20the%20technical%20organization%20and%20for%20their%20support%20throughout%20the%20years.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThere's%20never%20an%20ideal%20time%20to%20step%20away%20from%20a%20place%20one%20cherishes%2C%20yet%20this%20moment%20feels%20right.%20Our%20recent%20releases%20of%20speech-to-speech%20and%20OpenAl%20o1%20mark%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20era%20in%20interaction%20and%20intelligence%20-%20achievements%20made%20possible%20by%20your%20ingenuity%20and%20craftsmanship.%20We%20didn't%20merely%20build%20smarter%20models%2C%20we%20fundamentally%20changed%20how%20Al%20systems%20learn%20and%20reason%20through%20complex%20problems.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWe%20brought%20safety%20research%20from%20the%20theoretical%20realm%20into%20practical%20applications%2C%20creating%20models%20that%20are%20more%20robust%2C%20aligned%2C%20and%20steerable%20than%20ever%20before.%20Our%20work%20has%20made%20cutting-edge%20Al%20research%20intuitive%20and%20accessible%2C%20developing%20technology%20that%20adapts%20and%20evolves%20based%20on%20everyone's%20input.%20This%20success%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20our%20outstanding%20teamwork%2C%20and%20it%20is%20because%20of%20your%20brilliance%2C%20your%20dedication%2C%20and%20your%20commitment%20that%20OpenAl%20stands%20at%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20Al%20innovation.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI'm%20stepping%20away%20because%20I%20want%20to%20create%20the%20time%20and%20space%20to%20do%20my%20own%20exploration.%20For%20now%2C%20my%20primary%20focus%20is%20doing%20everything%20in%20my%20power%20to%20ensure%20a%20smooth%20transition%2C%20maintaining%20the%20momentum%20we've%20built.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20will%20forever%20be%20grateful%20for%20the%20opportunity%20to%20build%20and%20work%20alongside%20this%20remarkable%20team.%20Together%2C%20we've%20pushed%20the%20boundaries%20of%20scientific%20understanding%20in%20our%20quest%20to%20improve%20human%20well-being.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWhile%20I%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20in%20the%20trenches%20with%20you%2C%20I%20will%20still%20be%20rooting%20for%20you%20all.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWith%20deep%20gratitude%20for%20the%20friendships%20forged%2C%20the%20triumphs%20achieved%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20the%20challenges%20overcome%20together.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMira%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fsama%2Fstatus%2F1839028518996324755%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20had%20thanked%20Murati%20in%20a%20message%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20overstate%20how%20much%20Mira%20has%20meant%20to%20OpenAI%2C%20our%20mission%2C%20and%20to%20us%20all%20personally%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20tremendous%20gratitude%20towards%20her%20for%20what%20she%20has%20helped%20us%20build%20and%20accomplish%2C%20but%20I%20most%20of%20all%20feel%20personal%20gratitude%20towards%20her%20for%20the%20support%20and%20love%20during%20all%20the%20hard%20times.%20I%20am%20excited%20for%20what%20she'll%20do%20next.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMurati%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-mira-murati-openai-new-interim-ceo-2023-11%5C%22%20t