7-9271-af19dbfac511%5C%22%3ELive%20podcasts%20and%20themed%20events%20help%20creators%20build%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20the%20creator-talent-firm%20Snapback%20Agency%20hosted%20a%20basketball-themed%20event%20at%20the%20Mall%20of%20America%20with%20several%20of%20its%20athlete-creator%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESnapback%20Agency%20ran%20the%20event%20in%20partnership%20with%20Mall%20of%20America%2C%20and%20creators%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjennabandy21%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJenna%20Bandy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstrictlybball%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStrictly%20Bball%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbrianagreen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBree%20Green%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcarson.roney%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECarson%20Roney%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20such%20a%20powerful%20connection%20for%20people%20to%20show%20up%20in%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alex%20Sheinman%2C%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Snapback%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreators%20are%20also%20touring%20the%20country%20to%20cities%20with%20the%20most%20engaged%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20comedians%20Claire%20Parker%20and%20Ashley%20Hamilton%20host%20the%20podcast%C2%A0Celebrity%20Memoir%20Book%20Club%20(CMBC)%2C%20where%20they%20discuss%20celebrity%20memoirs.%20Parker%20and%20Hamilton%20have%20taken%20their%20podcast%20on%20the%20road%2C%20touring%20cities%20around%20the%20US%20to%20meet%20their%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20prefer%20the%20intimacy%20and%20the%20camaraderie%20of%20all%20being%20in%20a%20space%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamilton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurating%20a%20space%20where%20their%20fans%20can%20meet%20each%20other%20is%20also%20a%20driving%20force%20behind%20CMBC's%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20major%20undertone%20of%20our%20podcast%20is%20female%20friendship%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hamilton%2C%20who%20became%20friends%20with%20cohost%20Claire%20in%20her%20mid-20s.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20really%20notable%20push%20right%20now%2C%20or%20desire%20from%20people%2C%20to%20make%20more%20deep%20friendships%20in%20their%20late%2020s%2C%20early%2030s%2C%2040s%2C%20and%20beyond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20an%20entire%20crop%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firl-social-startups-combat-loneliness-among-millennials-gen-z-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estartups%20and%20events%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20American%20cities%20are%20trying%20to%20tackle%20this%20hunger%20for%20adult%20friendship%20amid%20a%20so-called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-loneliness-technology-ai-social-media-spending-inflation-millennials-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloneliness%3C%2Fa%3E%20epidemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCreating%20these%20spaces%20where%20people%20can%20gather%20in%20real%20life%2C%20where%20the%20common%20interest%20is%20our%20podcast%2C%20is%20such%20a%20great%20jumping-off%20point%20for%20helping%20people%20meet%20other%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamilton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20each%20live%20show%2C%20Hamilton%20and%20Parker%20also%20like%20to%20host%20meetups%20where%20they%20can%20chat%20one-on-one%20with%20their%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20love%20to%20let%20people%20gather%20before%20the%20show%20so%20that%20if%20they%20buy%20a%20ticket%20alone%2C%20they%20can%20come%20and%20make%20friends%20on%20their%20way%20into%20the%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamilton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreators%20are%20following%20the%20steps%20of%20traditional%20media%20by%20bringing%20their%20audience%20together%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn-person%20concerts%20have%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-music-survey-users-more-likely-to-attend-concerts-stream-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecentral%20to%20revenue%20in%20the%20music%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20now%20entertainment%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-house-disney-world-theme-parks-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20in-person%20experiences%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too.%20Theme%20parks%20have%20always%20been%20a%20key%20part%20of%20Disney%20and%20Universal's%20in-person%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Celebrity%20Memoir%20Book%20Club%20podcast%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f437210d59cc64f5b018c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223018%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClaire%20Parker%20and%20Ashley%20Hamilton%20recently%20went%20on%20tour%20with%20their%20podcast%20Celebrity%20Memoir%20Book%20Club.%3Cp%3ECelebrity%20Memoir%20Book%20Club%2C%20Vox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b1a3c363-5c7e-47d2-ba38-19d8e4a4bd64%5C%22%3ECreators%20are%20linking%20up%20with%20tech%20and%20media%20companies%20to%20bring%20fans%20offline%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECreator-led%20in-person%20events%20aren't%20completely%20new.%20In%20the%20pre-pandemic%20era%2C%20some%20YouTube%20stars%20would%20go%20on%20tours%2C%20planning%20shows%20that%20resembled%20more%20of%20a%20variety%20show.%20In%202015%2C%20YouTube%20creators%20Dan%20Howell%20and%20Phil%20Lester%20went%20on%20tour%20timed%20with%20the%20release%20of%20their%20book.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFouELh6S1co%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHowell%20and%20Lester%20performed%3C%2Fa%3E%20challenges%20onstage%20and%20various%20skits%2C%20like%20giving%20advice%20to%20audience%20members%20and%20reading%20fan%20fiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20creators%20are%20reimagining%20how%20to%20interact%20with%20their%20fans%20and%20create%20more%20intimacy%20with%20their%20audiences.%20And%20it%20takes%20more%20than%20just%20getting%20fans%20in%20a%20room%20for%20an%20in-person%20experience%20to%20be%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20help%20in%20putting%20on%20these%20events%2C%20creators%20have%20turned%20to%20companies%20ranging%20from%20the%20upstart%20event%20app%20Posh%2C%20to%20the%20digital-media%20stalwart%20Vox%20Media%2C%20to%20the%20buzzy%20subscription%20platform%20Substack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvents%20app%20Posh%2C%20which%20recently%20raised%20a%20%2422%20million%20round%20of%20funding%2C%20has%20been%20used%20by%20creators%20to%20organize%20and%20monetize%20IRL%20events.%20Creators%20can%20organize%20events%20using%20Posh%2C%20sell%20tickets%2C%20and%20have%20their%20events%20promoted%20in%20an%20in-app%20feed%20of%20event%20recommendations.%20For%20instance%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-creator-earns-tiktok-instagram-events-brand-deals-podcast-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAriana%20Nathani%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20creator%20behind%20the%20%26quot%3BDrinks%20First%26quot%3B%20dating%20podcast%2C%20hosts%20events%20in%20NYC%20using%20Posh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVox%20Media%20has%20also%20doubled%20down%20on%20investing%20in%20podcasting%20and%20is%20helping%20its%20podcast%20creators%20expand%20into%20live%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJackie%20Cinguina%2C%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20and%20Lillian%20Xu%2C%20executive%20director%2C%20spoke%20with%20BI%20about%20the%20company's%20offerings%20for%20podcast%20creators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVox%20Media%2C%20which%20works%20with%20Celebrity%20Memoir%20Book%20Club%2C%20has%20a%20production%20team%20that%20collaborates%20with%20podcast%20talent%20and%20producers%20when%20planning%20a%20live%20event%2C%20Cinguina%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVox%20Media%20leans%20on%20specific%20marketing%2C%20like%20placing%20podcast%20talent%20into%20larger%20in-person%20events%20to%20perform%2C%20like%20South%20by%20Southwest.%20This%20year%2C%20Vox%20Media%20programmed%20the%20conference's%20podcasting%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20Vox%20hosted%20several%20virtual%20events%2C%20but%20they%20didn't%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20complete%20replacement%20for%20the%20energy%20created%20by%20an%20in-person%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20an%20audience%20standpoint%2C%20we%20thought%20it%20was%20really%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Xu%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20about%20bringing%20back%20live%20events.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20podcaster%20perspective%2C%20we%20saw%20that%20they're%20often%20able%20to%20test%20new%20formats%20or%20try%20things%20out%20in%20front%20of%20a%20live%20audience%20and%20get%20that%20real-time%20reaction.%20And%20that%20gives%20them%20a%20lot%20of%20energy.%20You%20see%20them%20react%20to%20the%20audience%20and%20feed%20off%20of%20them%20when%20they%20are%20in%20front%20of%20a%20live%20audience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubstack%2C%20too%2C%20is%20finding%20its%20footing%20in%20the%20IRL%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20the%20newsletter%20platform%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20worked%20to%20strengthen%20its%20podcast%20play%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20helped%20several%20creators%20host%20events%2C%20such%20as%20live%20readings%20hosted%20by%20writers%20like%20Delia%20Cai%2C%20a%20quiz%20show%20hosted%20by%20Hunter%20Harris%2C%20and%20a%20fashion%20week%20experience%20with%20Emilia%20Petrarca.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSubstack%20is%20fundamentally%20built%20in%20these%20direct%20relationships%20between%20publisher%20and%20subscriber%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20head%20of%20writer%20relations%20Sophia%20Efthimiatou.%20%26quot%3BIt%20creates%20a%20very%20intimate%20and%20strong%20bond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20ticket%20sales%20are%20a%20clear%20mark%20of%20success%20for%20events%20like%20those%20put%20on%20by%20Substack%20(some%20of%20wh