ai-2023-5%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNvidia%2520CEO%2520Jensen%2520Huang%2520is%2520now%2520worth%2520%2524102.8%2520billion.%26amp%3Btext%3DMost%2520of%2520Huang%2527s%2520wealth%2520comes%2Cthe%2520generative%2520AI%2520boom%2520continues.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20one%20of%20several%20big%20names%20to%20try%20out%20Meta's%20new%20Orion%20prototype%20glasses%20in%20a%20video%20shown%20at%20Meta's%20Connect%20event%20on%20Wednesday%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20fan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20demonstrate%20the%20good%20impression%20the%20glasses%20have%20had%20on%20those%20who%20have%20tried%20them%2C%20Meta%20CEO%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20screened%20a%20video%20of%20people's%20reactions%20after%20wearing%20them.%20The%20video%20featured%20prominent%20Silicon%20Valley%20names%2C%20media%20personalities%2C%20and%20Olympians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nvidia%20CEO%2C%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20testers%2C%20referred%20to%20the%20glasses'%20100-gram%20weight%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20big%20deal%26quot%3B%20and%20complimented%20various%20aspects%20of%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tracking%20is%20good%2C%20the%20brightness%20is%20good%2C%20the%20color%20contrast%20is%20good%2C%20field%20of%20view%20is%20excellent%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%20in%20the%20video%20shown%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Orion%20glasses%20are%20the%20company's%20first%20prototype%20of%20full%20holographic%20augmented%20reality%2C%20and%20Zuckerberg%20referred%20to%20them%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20advanced%20glasses%20the%20world%20has%20ever%20seen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20started%20putting%20together%20a%20team%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%20people%20in%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20about%20a%20decade%20ago%20to%20build%20the%20glasses%2C%20he%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20technical%20challenges%20to%20making%20them%20were%20%26quot%3Binsane.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20physical%20world%20where%20holograms%20overlayed%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-earnings-q4-2023-mark-zuckerberg-hiring-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMeta%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20CEO%20named%20several%20of%20the%20challenges%20with%20building%20the%20glasses%2C%20like%20the%20need%20for%20a%20wide%20field%20of%20view%20while%20keeping%20them%20light.%20He%20added%20that%20you%20needed%20to%20be%20able%20to%20see%20through%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20said%20the%20glasses%20were%20made%20from%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20display%20architecture%20that%20uses%20tiny%20projectors%20that%20bend%20light%20to%20create%20holograms%20of%20different%20depths%20and%20sizes.%20The%20glasses%20are%20powered%20by%20a%20battery%20in%20the%20arm%2C%20made%20of%20customized%20silicon%20and%20sensors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Orion%20holographic%20glasses%20weren't%20ready%20for%20consumers%20yet%20as%20Meta%20was%20refining%20some%20of%20the%20details%20and%20working%20on%20lowering%20the%20retail%20price.%20However%2C%20some%20external%20developers%20will%20be%20able%20to%20get%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang's%20compliments%20are%20somewhat%20of%20a%20big%20deal.%20Nvidia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20valuable%20companies%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20its%20graphics%20processing%20units%20are%20powering%20the%20AI%20revolution.%20Given%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-price-earnings-party-investors-cult-investing-memes-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany's%20cultlike%20following%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Huang's%20words%20also%20carry%20a%20lot%20of%20weight%20in%20the%20tech%20world%20and%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20Zuckerberg%20is%20a%20big%20Nvidia%20client.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-ai-flex-meta-nvidia-gpus-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Meta%20CEO%20has%20bragged%20about%20stockpiling%20GPUs%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20build%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20amount%20of%20infrastructure%26quot%3B%20to%20further%20the%20company's%20artificial-intelligence%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20The%20Verge%2C%20Zuckerberg%20said%20that%20when%20Meta's%20Nvidia%20components%20and%20other%20AI%20chips%20were%20accounted%20for%2C%20Meta%20would%20have%20nearly%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F1%2F18%2F24042354%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-agi-reorg-interview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E600%2C000%20GPUs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20declined%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-jensen-huang-fan-of-meta-orion-prototype-glasses-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727294605000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f450190d59cc64f5b02cb0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-jensen-huang-fan-of-meta-orion-prototype-glasses-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20was%20featured%20in%20a%20reaction%20video%20complimenting%20the%20features%20of%20Meta's%20new%20Orion%20prototype%20glasses%2C%20and%20he%20seemed%20to%20approve.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-jensen-huang-fan-of-meta-orion-prototype-glasses-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22