%3Etwo-day%20train%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20had%20the%20choice%20between%20two%20classes%3A%20SilverLeaf%20and%20SilverLeaf%20Plus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20a%20SilverLeaf%20ticket%20on%20my%20route%20cost%20%241%2C465%20for%20a%20solo%20traveler%20and%20included%20meals%2C%20alcohol%2C%20a%20seat%20in%20a%20train%20car%20with%20glass-dome%20windows%2C%20and%20a%20hotel%20room%20for%20an%20overnight%20stop%20in%20Glenwood%20Springs%2C%20Colorado.%20In%202024%2C%20the%20SilverLeaf%20ticket%20cost%20%241%2C699.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrain%20riders%20could%20upgrade%20to%20SilverLeaf%20Plus%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-class-first-time-flying-surprising-things-photos-2023-1%5C%22%3Eakin%20to%20first%20class%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20about%20%24550%20more.%20In%202024%2C%20SilverLeaf%20Plus%20tickets%20sell%20for%20%242%2C269%20and%20grant%20travelers%20access%20to%20a%20dedicated%20lounge%20car%2C%20elevated%20dinner%20service%2C%20and%20a%20hotel%20room%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20downtown%20Glenwood%20Springs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20a%20look%20at%20what%20the%20elevated%20experience%20is%20like.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20a%20thrifty%20traveler%2C%20I%20purchased%20a%20standard%20SilverLeaf%20ticket.%20But%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20two-day%20trip%2C%20Rocky%20Mountaineer's%20manager%2C%20Zach%20Lucas%2C%20gave%20me%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20entire%20train%2C%20allowing%20me%20to%20peek%20inside%20the%20first-class%20car.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Train%20manager%20Zach%20Lucas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F629793f43efa8c0019aa79dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrain%20manager%20Zach%20Lucas.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETogether%2C%20Lucas%20and%20I%20walked%20from%20my%20standard%20SilverLeaf%20train%