20land%20former%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20in%20trouble%2C%20his%20ex-officer%20on%20special%20duty%20(OSD)%20Lokesh%20Sharma%20has%20held%20him%20responsible%20for%20phone%20tapping%20during%20the%20political%20crisis%20in%20the%20state%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Mr%20Gehlot%20should%20be%20interrogated%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%20questioned%20Mr%20Sharma%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20phone-tapping%20case%20lodged%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20Union%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20questioning%2C%20Mr%20Sharma%20said%20he%20submitted%20a%20seven-page%20written%20statement%2C%20describing%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20on%20July%2016%2C%202020%2C%20when%20he%20got%20a%20pen%20drive%20containing%20call%20recordings%20from%20the%20then%20chief%20minister%20for%20circulating%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Mr%20Gehlot%20could%20tell%20how%20he%20got%20the%20call%20recordings%20and%20whether%20the%20call%20interceptions%20were%20done%20legally%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma's%20claim%20this%20time%20has%20marked%20a%20shift%20from%20his%20previous%20stand%20that%20he%20had%20got%20three%20audio%20clips%20from%20social%20media%20and%20forwarded%20those%20to%20media%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%20was%20called%20for%20questioning%20at%20Delhi%20Police's%20Crime%20Branch%20office%20at%20Rohini.%20He%20reached%20there%20around%2011%20am%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%2C%20in%20April%20this%20year%2C%20had%20publicly%20alleged%20that%20an%20audio%20clip%20of%20a%20purported%20telephonic%20conversation%20between%20Mr%20Shekhawat%20and%20some%20Congress%20leaders%20on%20%26quot%3Btoppling%26quot%3B%20the%20then%20Congress%20government%20in%20Rajasthan%20in%202020%20was%20given%20to%20him%20by%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20he%20mentioned%20this%20in%20the%20written%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20stated%20that%20the%20then%20chief%20minister%20had%20called%20me%20at%20the%20chief%20minister's%20residence%20and%20gave%20me%20a%20pen%20drive.%20He%20directed%20me%20to%20circulate%20the%20content%20of%20the%20pen%20drive%20to%20newspapers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20home%2C%20transferred%20the%20files%20from%20the%20pen%20drive%20to%20my%20laptop%20and%20from%20laptop%20to%20my%20phone%2C%20then%20circulated%20them%20to%20media%20houses%20as%20directed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20crime%20branch%20should%20now%20summon%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20for%20questioning%20to%20know%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20next%20course%20of%20investigation%20should%20involve%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%20said%20that%20he%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20call%20interceptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20done%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20then%20chief%20minister.%20Now%20he%20can%20disclose%20further%20details%2C%20how%20the%20interception%20was%20done%2C%20and%20whether%20it%20was%20legal%20or%20illegal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%20claimed%20that%20phones%20of%20several%20Congress%20MLAs%2C%20from%20both%20camps%20of%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20Sachin%20Pilot%2C%20were%20intercepted%20at%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20during%20the%20political%20crisis%20and%20he%20used%20to%20get%20a%20transcription%20of%20each%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20then%20chief%20secretary%2C%20DGP%2C%20home%20secretary%20and%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%20were%20all%20aware%20of%20the%20developments%20related%20to%20phone%20tapping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20phone-tapping%20controversy%20erupted%20in%20July%202020%20during%20a%20political%20crisis%20when%20the%20Congress%20