ven%20flew%20to%20Washington%20DC%20to%20meet%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20The%20two%20leaders%20reportedly%20discussed%20Ukraine's%20use%20of%20weapons%20on%20Russian%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20intelligence%20had%20information%20about%20such%20a%20possibility%20and%20had%20said%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20become%20necessary%20for%20Moscow%20to%20revise%20its%20nuclear%20doctrine%20because%20of%20the%20West's%20escalation%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20reports%20that%20the%20United%20States%20and%20United%20Kingdom%20are%20about%20to%20give%20clearance%20to%20Ukraine%20for%20Kyiv%20to%20launch%20cruise%20missiles%20on%20Russian%20soil%2C%20President%20Putin%20said%20this%20month%20that%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20West%20would%20be%20directly%20fighting%20with%20Russia%20if%20it%20gave%20such%20permission%20to%20Ukraine%20(to%20bomb%20Russia)%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20Moscow%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20make%20%26quot%3Bappropriate%20decisions%26quot%3B%20in%20such%20a%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERUSSIA'S%20NUCLEAR%20DOCTRINE%20%26amp%3B%20TREATY%20WITH%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20nuclear%20power.%20Together%2C%20Russia%20and%20the%20United%20States%20control%2088%25%20of%20the%20world's%20nuclear%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia's%20current%20nuclear%20doctrine%20was%20set%20in%20place%20by%20Vladimir%20Putin%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20before%20the%20war%20with%20Ukraine%20broke%20out.%20According%20to%20the%20current%20doctrine%2C%20Russia%20may%20use%20nuclear%20weapons%20in%20the%20scenario%20where%20it%20comes%20under%20a%20nuclear%20attack%20or%20if%20a%20conventional%20attack%20threatens%20the%20existence%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20and%20Russia%20have%20a%20nuclear%20treaty%20called%20the%20US-Russia%20New%20START%20Treaty%2C%20which%20entered%20into%20force%20on%20February%205%2C%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20treaty%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20Russian%20Federation%20had%20seven%20years%20to%20meet%20the%20treaty's%20central%20limits%20on%20strategic%20offensive%20arms%20(by%20February%205%2C%202018)%20and%20are%20then%20obligated%20to%20maintain%20those%20limits%20for%20as%20long%20as%20the%20treaty%20remains%20in%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20State%20Department%2C%20this%20treaty%20enhances%20US%20national%20security%20by%20placing%20verifiable%20limits%20on%20all%20Russian%20deployed%20intercontinental-range%20nuclear%20weapons.%20The%20United%20States%20and%20the%20Russian%20Federation%20have%20agreed%20to%20extend%20the%20treaty%20through%20February%204%2C%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Reuters%20report%2C%20the%20Kremlin%20said%20that%20any%20discussions%20about%20a%20replacement%20to%20the%20US-Russia%20New%20START%20Treaty%2C%20which%20expires%20in%202026%2C%20would%20need%20to%20take%20into%20account%20European%20nuclear%20potential%20-%20shorthand%20for%20the%20arsenals%20of%20Britain%20and%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20yet%20received%20a%20response%20from%20the%20Americans%20to%20this%2C%20but%20of%20course%20an%20agreement%20is%20needed%20and%20negotiations%20should%20begin%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Peskov%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20a%20possible%20replacement%20for%20the%20New%20START%20Treaty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20STORM%20SHADOW%20MISSILE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine%20already%20has%20the%20UK-supplied%20Storm%20Shadow%20missile%2C%20but%20uses%20it%20only%20within%20its%20territory%20to%20combat%20Russian%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20there%20are%20restriction%20on%20Ukraine%20on%20the%20use%20of%20advanced%20western%20weaponry%20on%20targets%20within%20the%20Russian%20territory%2C%20but%20this%20is%20likely%20to%20change%20with%20clearances%20reportedly%20being%20issued%20by%20the%20UK%2C%20with%20US%20backing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Storm%20Shadow%20is%20a%20low-observable%2C%20long-range%20air-launched%20cruise%20missile.%20It%20is%20jointly%20developed%20by%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20and%20France%20and%20has%20a%20range%20of%20around%20500%20km.%20It%20has%20already%20been%20integrated%20into%20Ukrainian%20fighter%20aircraft%2C%20including%20the%20Russia-built%20Su-24%20bombers%20-%20a%20legacy%20of%20the%20past%2C%20from%20when%20Ukraine%20was%20part%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Soviet%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeveloped%20in%201994%20and%20manufactured%20by%20Matra%20and%20British%20Aerospace%2C%20the%20Storm%20Shadow%20missile%20is%20now%20made%20by%20MBDA%20Systems.%20'Storm%20Shadow'%20is%20the%20weapon's%20British%20name%2C%20while%20in%20France%20it%20is%20called%20the%20SCALP-EG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERUSSIAN%20NUCLEAR%20WEAPONS%20STOCKPILE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20Ukraine%20use%20cruise%20missiles%20to%20attack%20Russian%20territory%2C%20a%20Russian%20response%20to%20this%20could%20be%20massive.%20The%20international%20worry%20is%20that%20Moscow%20may%20seriously%20consider%20the%20use%20of%20nuclear%20weapons%20in%20such%20a%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Center%20for%20Arms%20Control%20and%20Non-Proliferation%20-%20a%20nonpartisan%20non-profit%20organisation%20on%20nuclear%20weapons%20disarmament%20-%20Russia%20maintains%20a%20stockpile%20of%20an%20estimated%206%2C372%20nuclear%20warheads%20-%20the%20world's%20largest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20these%2C%201%2C572%20of%20which%20are%20deployed%20on%20strategic%20land-based%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20submarine-launched%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20and%20heavy%20bombers.%20Approximately%20870%20more%20strategic%20warheads%20and%201%2C870%20non-strategic%20warheads%20are%20in%20reserve%20with%20an%20additional%20estimated%202%2C060%20warheads%20awaiting%20dismantlement.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727287860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fvqg4p6a_vladimir-putin-reuters_625x300_25_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-to-consider-nuclear-response-in-event-of-massive-air-attack-putin-6649829%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vladimir%20Putin%20today%20issued%20a%20nuclear%20warning%20to%20the%20West%20in%20the%20event%20that%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%26quot%3B%20air%20attack%20on%20Russia.%20This%20includes%20the%20use%20of%20cruise%20missiles%20which%20the%20UK%20has%20supplied%20to%20Ukraine%20for%20Kyiv%20to%20target%20locations%20within%20Russian%20territory%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-to-consider-nuclear-response-in-event-of-massive-air-attack-putin-6649829%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Takers%20For%20Government%20Schools%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3F%205%2C000%20See%200%20Admissions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20slogan%20of%20the%20government's%20Sarva%20Shiksha%20Abhiyan%2C%20aimed%20at%20universal%20elementary%20education%2C%20is%20%3Cem%3E'Sab%20Padhe%2C%20Sab%20Badhe'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(everyone%20should%20study%2C%20everyone%20should%20grow)%2C%20but%20it%20appears%20that%20children%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20studying%20anywhere%20but%20in%20government%20schools%20-%20despite%20incentives%20like%20free%20uniforms%20and%20mid-day%20meals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20the%20state%20education%20department%2C%20more%20than%205%2C500%20government%20schools%20in%20the%20state%20reported%20zero%20admissions%20in%20Class%201%20this%20year%20and%20the%20situation%20doesn't%20get%20much%20better%20when%20more%20schools%20are%20taken%20into%20account.%20Around%2025%2C000%20schools%20have%20seen%20only%20one%20or%20two%20students%20enrol%20in%20the%20first%20grade%20and%20less%20than%2010%20students%20each%20have%20taken%20admission%20in%2011%2C345%20schools.%20These%20institutions%20add%20up%20to%20over%2041%2C000%20and%20account%20for%20over%2040%25%20of%20the%20total%2094%2C039%20government%20schools%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistricts%20like%20Seoni%2C%20Satna%2C%20Narsinghpur%2C%20Betul%2C%20Khargone%2C%20Sagar%2C%20Vidisha%2C%20Raisen%2C%20Mandsaur%2C%20and%20Dewas%20have%20seen%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20zero%20enrolments.%20These%20numbers%20suggest%20a%20significant%20shift%20in%20public%20trust%2C%20indicating%20that%20parents%20are%20increasingly%20turning%20away%20from%20government-run%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangal%20Tawde%2C%20a%20hotel%20employee%20and%20resident%20of%20Berasia%20near%20Bhopal%2C%20initially%20wanted%20to%20enrol%20his%20daughter%20in%20a%20government%20school.%20On%20visiting%20the%20institution%2C%20however%2C%20he%20found%20rainwater%20leaking%20from%20the%20roof%20of%20the%20dilapidated%20building%20and%20noted%20the%20shortage%20of%20teachers.%20Concerned%20about%20the%20poor%20conditions%2C%20Mangal%20chose%20to%20get%20his%20daughter%20admitted%20to%20a%20private%20school%20instead.%20Many%20other%20parents%20across%20the%20state%20have%20arrived%20at%20the%20same%20decision%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMissing%20Teachers%2C%20Poor%20Infra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpendra%20Kaushal%2C%20President%20of%20the%20State%20Teachers%20Association%2C%20said%20teachers%20are%20often%20assigned%20non-educational%20tasks%2C%20which%20severely%20disrupts%20the%20learning%20process.%20Teachers%20are%20also%20frequently%20attached%20to%20other%20departments%2C%20reducing%20their%20availability%20in%20classrooms.%20As%20many%20as%201%2C275%20across%2046%20districts%20have%20no%20permanent%20teachers%20at%20all%20and%206%2C838%20schools%20in%2047%20districts%20have%20only%20one%20teacher%20each.%20The%20gaps%20across%20the%20system%20are%20being%20plug