ng%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98It%20was%20heartbreaking%20to%20watch%20young%20children%20at%20work%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F180637%2Ftamil-nadu-gi-tag-kancheepuram-sari-lawyer-sanjai-gandhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHailed%20for%20its%20silk%20sarees%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kancheepuram%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20home%20to%20over%2060%2C000%20looms%20and%20over%2045%2C000%20weavers.%20Superficially%2C%20this%20is%20a%20matter%20to%20take%20pride%20in.%20A%20closer%20probe%20will%20unearth%20the%20harsh%20reality%20hidden%20in%20these%20statistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20closed%20loom%20doors%2C%20young%20children%20work%20hard%20to%20spin%20%3Cem%3Ezari%20%3C%2Fem%3E(gold%20thread)%20and%20silk%20into%20vibrant%20%3Cem%3Esarees%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20make%20their%20way%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversations%20with%20these%20children%20and%20their%20families%20led%20Dr%20Sankar%20to%20discover%20the%20root%20of%20this.%20%E2%80%9CChildren%2C%20traditionally%2C%20are%20a%20cheap%20source%20of%20labour.%20Families%20that%20have%20no%20permanent%20income%20send%20their%20children%20to%20work%20as%20bonded%20labourers%20in%20the%20weaving%20industry.%E2%80%9D%20In%20the%20tug-of-war%20between%20a%20decent%20livelihood%20and%20a%20square%20meal%2C%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20futures%20were%20caught%20in%20the%20crosshairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-2-1726670280.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Kalpana%20Sankar%20and%20philanthropist%20Percy%20Barnevik%20joined%20hands%20to%20champion%20change%20at%20grassroots%20level%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20communities%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-2-1726670280.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-2-1726670280-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-2-1726670280-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-2-1726670280-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-2-1726670280-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366605%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Kalpana%20Sankar%20and%20philanthropist%20Dr%20Percy%20Barnevik%20joined%20hands%20to%20champion%20change%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20communities%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20around%202004%2C%20another%20brilliant%20mind%20was%20troubled%20by%20this%20pressing%20issue.%20Swedish%20businessman%20and%20philanthropist%20Dr%20Percy%20Barnevik%20learnt%20about%20Dr%20Sankar%20%E2%80%94%20who%20was%20then%20working%20as%20a%20specialist%20for%20the%20UN%20agency%E2%80%99s%20International%20Fund%20for%20Agricultural%20Development.%20Barnevik%20approached%20Dr%20Sankar%20with%20a%20proposal%20to%20manage%20%E2%80%9Ca%20small%20charity%20working%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F281329%2Fchild-labour-women-empowerment-education-rural-development-bayer-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeradicate%20child%20labour%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Kancheepuram%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20said%20an%20immediate%20%E2%80%98yes%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20Hand%20in%20Hand%20India%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20were%20able%20to%20help%20most%20of%20them%20get%20their%20childhoods%20back%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20children%20needed%20a%20shift%20in%20their%20immediate%20realities%3B%20the%20duo%20figured%20that%20residential%20schools%20would%20be%20the%20best%20bet%20to%20free%20them%20from%20the%20labour%20force.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20eight%20residential%20schools%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20where%20the%20curriculum%20focused%20on%20Tamil%20and%20English%20literature%2C%20mathematics%2C%20physical%20education%2C%20and%20activity-based%20learning.%20We%20also%20invested%20in%20the%20kids%E2%80%99%20counselling%20and%20would%20track%20their%20progress%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time.%20Nearly%2040%2C000%20children%20benefited%20from%20these%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Sankar%20notes.%20But%2C%20she%20says%2C%20they%20deduced%20that%20broader%20social%20sensitisation%20was%20needed%20to%20tackle%20the%20issue%20of%20child%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20in%20time%2C%20the%20vision%20was%20extrapolated%20to%20the%20kids%E2%80%99%20families%20too.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20to%20address%20issues%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F127941%2Fhimachali-health-worker-vaccinate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommunity%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20skills%20development%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20job%20creation.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20a%20pan-Indian%20NGO%20rewriting%20the%20story%20of%20rural%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Sankar%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-3-1726670406.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Percy%20Barnevik%20(L)%20and%20Dr%20Kalpana%20Sankar%20(R)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-3-1726670406.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-3-1726670406-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-3-1726670406-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-3-1726670406-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-3-1726670406-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366607%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Percy%20Barnevik%20and%20Dr%20Kalpana%20Sankar%20have%20been%20reaching%20out%20to%20rural%20communities%20across%20India%20through%20Hand%20in%20Hand%20India%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20day.%20A%20call%20from%20one%20of%20the%20children%20%E2%80%94%20informing%20her%20about%20a%20job%20they%20have%20secured%20or%20sharing%20a%20life%20event%20with%20her%20%E2%80%94%20manages%20to%20light%20up%20Dr%20Sankar%E2%80%99s%20mood.%20Point%20this%20out%20to%20her%20and%20she%20says%20it%20is%20all%20the%20validation%20she%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20Meera%E2%80%99s%20story%20for%20instance.%20Meera%20was%20identified%20by%20the%20Child%20Labour%20Elimination%20Programme%20(CLEP)%20field%20staff%20in%202013.%20The%20family%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98scheduled%20tribe%E2%80%99%20status%20meant%20they%20were%20ostracised%20from%20society%20and%20Meera%20and%20her%20siblings%20were%20compelled%20to%20take%20up%20odd%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20working%20at%20brick%20kilns%2C%20cutting%20forest%20wood%2C%20and%20grazing%20cattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hand%20in%20Hand%20India%20team%20encouraged%20Meera%E2%80%99s%20parents%20to%20enrol%20her%20and%20her%20three%20siblings%20at%20the%20Dhamaneri%20Residential%20Special%20Training%20Centre%20(RSTC)%20in%20Tiruvallur%20district.%20The%20team%20then%20coaxed%20M