ttps%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-1726841838.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D366915%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22You%20know%20him%20as%20the%20man%20behind%20the%20'Selfie%20With%20Daughter'%20campaign.%20But%20Sunil%20Jaglan's%20impact%20goes%20far%20beyond%20viral%20fame.%20Discover%20how%20his%20Bibipur%20model%20of%20village%20development%20became%20a%20global%20example%20of%20progress%2C%20transforming%20lives%20and%20inspiring%20change%20beyond%20his%20village.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366915%2Fsunil-jaglan-selfie-with-daughter-bibipur-village-haryana-daughters-day-women-empowerment-female-foeticide%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20a%20Couple%20Fought%20Relentless%20Battles%20to%20Demand%20Justice%20After%20Whistleblower%20Manjunath%E2%80%99s%20Murder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mentions%20of%20murder%20and%20violence%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E1980s%2C%20Kolar%2C%20Karnataka%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20brothers%2C%20Manjunath%20and%20Raghavendra%20Shanmugam%2C%20were%20returning%20from%20school.%20As%20they%20chatted%2C%20Manjunath%20told%20his%20younger%20brother%20how%20he%20had%20stopped%20a%20classmate%20from%20bullying%20another%20student.%20This%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20this%20young%20boy%20had%20dared%20to%20question%20what%20was%20clearly%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENovember%202005%2C%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20same%20righteous%20boy%20was%20now%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307264%2Fgps-renewables-mainak-chakraborty-sreekrishna-sankar-ev-charging-station-biogas-to-electricity%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIIM%20graduate%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20and%20a%20sales%20officer%20at%20the%20Indian%20Oil%20Corporation%20(IOC).%20One%20of%20his%20responsibilities%20was%20checking%20petrol%20adulteration%20at%20petrol%20pumps.%20He%20set%20out%20on%20a%20tour%20of%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20district%20in%20November%202005.%20He%20found%20anomalies%2C%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%20at%20the%20Mittal%20Automobile%20Petrol%20Pump%20and%20was%20about%20to%20take%20measures%20to%20seal%20it.%20On%20the%20night%20of%2019%20November%2C%20he%20was%20murdered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManjunath%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20who%20were%20attending%20a%20family%20function%20in%20Chennai%2C%20were%20shocked%20beyond%20words.%20How%20could%20they%20even%20begin%20to%20fathom%20such%20an%20unjust%20shooting%20%E2%80%94%20where%20their%20son%E2%80%99s%20life%20was%20cut%20short%20for%20simply%20standing%20up%20for%20what%20was%20right%3F%20As%20they%20grappled%20with%20the%20loss%20of%20their%2027-year-old%20son%2C%20the%20news%20sent%20shockwaves%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hundred%20kilometres%20away%2C%20in%20Mysuru%2C%20a%20young%20couple%2C%20Anjali%20Mullatti%20and%20H%20Jaishankar%2C%20watched%20the%20news%20unfold%20on%20their%20TV%20screens.%20As%20IIM%20alumni%20themselves%2C%20they%20were%20shocked.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20anger%2C%20grief%2C%20and%20frustration%20within%20the%20IIM%20alumni%20groups%20across%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Calcutta%2C%20and%20Lucknow%20%E2%80%94%20the%20four%20IIMs%20at%20that%20time.%20While%20many%20vented%20their%20grief%20and%20anger%2C%20no%20one%20seemed%20to%20be%20doing%20anything%20on%20the%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20decided%20they%20would%20take%20action%20if%20no%20one%20else%20did.%20Their%20efforts%20led%20them%20to%20Kamini%20Jaiswal%2C%20a%20prominent%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%2C%20who%20connected%20them%20with%20criminal%20lawyer%20I%20B%20Singh%20in%20Luck