hool%20plays%20and%20dance%20competitions.%20The%20turning%20point%20came%20in%20college%20when%20a%20National%20School%20of%20Drama%20(NSD)%20alumnus%20noticed%20her%20talent.%20Encouraged%2C%20she%20enrolled%20in%20NSD%2C%20where%20three%20years%20of%20intensive%20training%20prepared%20her%20for%20the%20challenges%20ahead%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20ironclad%20commitment%20and%20a%20modest%20sum%20of%20Rs%2030%2C000%2C%20Sunita%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20in%20the%20late%2090s%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F266671%2Fsardar-udham-richard-klein-bollywood-actor-teacher-california%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edreaming%20of%20making%20it%20big%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20life%20in%20the%20city%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%20She%20struggled%20as%20a%20junior%20artist%2C%20often%20sharing%20cramped%2C%20dirty%20rooms%20with%20fellow%20actors.%20There%20were%20days%20when%20she%20waited%20for%20hours%20for%20a%20role%2C%20only%20to%20be%20typecast%20as%20a%20maid%20in%20small%20productions.%20Frustrated%2C%20she%20quit%20acting%20for%20two%20years%2C%20disillusioned%20by%20the%20repetitive%20roles%20being%20offered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20Sunita%20began%20to%20question%20her%20future%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20fate%20intervened.%20A%20call%20for%20an%20audition%20led%20her%20to%20the%20role%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBittu%20ki%20mummy%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20in%20%3Cem%3EGullak%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20series%20became%20an%20instant%20hit%2C%20with%20audiences%20praising%20Sunita%E2%80%99s%20impeccable%20portrayal%20of%20the%20nosy%2C%20hilarious%20neighbour.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20this%2C%20I%20used%20to%20do%20small%20roles%2C%20so%20when%20I%20found%20out%20about%20%3Cem%3EGullak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%E2%80%99s%20film%20career%20began%20with%20roles%20in%20%3Cem%3EEk%20Chalis%20Ki%20Last%20Local%2C%3C%2F